entry.tran: 无望成功的计划(或想法)
entry.def: If you describe a plan or idea as a non-starter, you mean that it has no chance of success.

example.ex: The United States is certain to reject the proposal as a non-starter...
example.tran: 美国肯定会以无成功希望为由拒绝这项提案。

example.ex: Some of the points that she put were indeed non-starters but some of them were really quite reasonable.
